OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The children hear the dogs snarling    
OL,6, outside, just beyond the flimsy plastic
OL,7, of the tent.                           
OL,9,FThe seven children of Rehab Abu Daqqa  
OL,10,Fcrowd around their mother. She is the  
OL,11,Flast safe harbour in their lives. They 
OL,12,Fhave shared things, these children and 
OL,13,Ftheir mother, which cannot be          
OL,14,Fcommunicated to those who have not seen
OL,15,Fthe things they have seen. Is there a  
OL,16,Fword to express what a child feels     
OL,17,Fknowing that just a few yards away,    
OL,18,Fanimals are dragging a body from a     
OL,19,Fgrave?                                 
